				<td colspan="2"><span><blockquote><b>Quote:</b><br><span class="quote">As far as I know sitting does nothing for our mana regeneration as we have a capped meditation skill of (1). I have never noticed a difference in standing and sitting mana regen.</span></blockquote>
<br />

<br />
Sitting gives you one more point of regen. 
<br />

<br />
With no FT items, AA's or spells/songs Standing recovery rate is 1 point.
<br />
With no FT items, AA's or spells/songs Sitting recovery rate is 2.
<br />

<br />
Don't believe me Try it. Hit your inventoury screen and check out your manna regen standing and sitting. You will notice a diferance of 1. When looking at a recovery bar it is hard to tell. However You have a number in your Inv screen and you can observe the diferance there.
<br />

